---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Meet Our Expert Dentists in Footscray | Multilingual & Caring Dental Team"
  description="Get to know our experienced and friendly dentists, led by Dr. David Cui, at Top Dentists Footscray. Trusted by the community since the 1990s, our multilingual team offers personalized care in English, Vietnamese, Chinese, Korean, Japanese, and Arabic."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Dentists</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
          Meet our experienced, friendly dentists
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our team, led by our principal dentist Dr David Cui are experienced, friendly and caring. Many of our patients have been with us since the 1990's and following them their families and friends. Be assured our dentists will do everything they can to care for you and we pride ourselves on the many patients that return to us year on year.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          To cater for the area's multicultural community, English, Vietnamese, Chinese, Korean, Japanese and Arabic are spoken by our dentists at Top Dentists Footscray.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        
        <!-- Dr David Cui -->
        <div class="card p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 observe-fade">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/david.jpg"
              alt="Dr David Cui - Principal Dentist at Top Dentists Footscray"
              width="339"
              height="339"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">
            Dr David Cui
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium mb-2">Principal Dentist</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-6">English/Mandarin</p>
          
          <div class="text-left space-y-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              As a local, David's earliest memories of Footscray are eating banh mi from Nhu Lan and shopping at the Little Saigon market with his parents. With over 10 years of experience, David believes his greatest strength is his ability to rapidly build rapport and trust with all patients.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              He has been described by his fellow colleagues and patients as a relatable, down-to-earth dentist with an easy manner. David is experienced in all aspects of dental work, ranging from direct restorations, endodontics, fixed/removable prosthodontics, preventive dentistry, exodontia, and working with children.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr Maluki Fernando -->
        <div class="card p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 observe-fade">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/maluki.jpg"
              alt="Dr Maluki Fernando - Dentist at Top Dentists Footscray"
              width="341"
              height="341"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">
            Dr Maluki Fernando
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium mb-2">Dentist</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-6">English</p>
          
          <div class="text-left space-y-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Maluki graduated with a Doctor of Dental Surgery from the University of Melbourne after a childhood ambition to be a dentist. Maluki operates with a focus on patient care and has a passion for helping people.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              As a dentist, her goal is to provide the highest quality treatment for patients while maintaining excellent clinical skills and providing empathy and understanding. She particularly enjoys working with families, promoting oral health and wellbeing at all ages, and has a special interest in preventative care for children and the extraction of difficult teeth.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Alongside working in private clinics, Maluki is currently studying for her Graduate Diploma in Dental Public Health.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr Charlie Li -->
        <div class="card p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 observe-fade">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/charlie-20-3-.jpg"
              alt="Dr Charlie Li - Dentist at Top Dentists Footscray"
              width="347"
              height="347"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">
            Dr Charlie Li
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium mb-2">Dentist</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-6">English/Mandarin/Shanghainese/Japanese</p>
          
          <div class="text-left space-y-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              After completing his VCE as dux of his year at Carey Grammar School, Charlie obtained his Doctor of Dental Surgery from the University of Melbourne. He has been working in private practices across Melbourne suburbs and enjoys all aspects of dentistry, with a particular interest in preventative dentistry.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Charlie prides himself on providing exceptional service to patients and always takes the time to carefully and fully explain available treatment options.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr Sharifa Tartoussi -->
        <div class="card p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 observe-fade">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/shrifa.jpg"
              alt="Dr Sharifa Tartoussi - Dentist at Top Dentists Footscray"
              width="350"
              height="350"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">
            Dr Sharifa Tartoussi
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium mb-2">Dentist</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-6">English/Arabic</p>
          
          <div class="text-left space-y-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Sharifa holds a Doctor of Dental Surgery from the University of Melbourne and has gained extensive experience working in both rural and metropolitan areas throughout Victoria. She understands that every patient is unique and strives to create tailored dental experiences that consider each individual's needs.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Sharifa firmly believes in person-centered, high-quality oral healthcare and works to create a comfortable environment where patients feel empowered to make informed decisions about their care. She is committed to building strong dentist-patient relationships and working collaboratively towards the shared goal of dental health in a way that puts the patient first.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Languages Spoken Section -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 text-center observe-fade">
        <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
            Languages We Speak
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            {[
              "English",
              "Mandarin Chinese", 
              "Shanghainese",
              "Japanese",
              "Arabic",
              "Vietnamese"
            ].map(language => (
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
                <span class="text-neutral-700 font-medium">{language}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-6 leading-relaxed">
            Our multilingual team ensures comfortable communication for our diverse Footscray community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Ready to Meet Our Team?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          To organise an appointment please call
          <a
            href="tel:+61396875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          or press here to book online
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
